videos.headline: London Perrantes continues hot start with and-one basket
California's Jabari Bird hits the and-one shot as he's falling to the court

videos.description: 2H (15:25) CAL Ivan Rabb made Dunk. Assisted by Charlie Moore.
videos.headline: Charlie Moore lobs up an alley-oop to Ivan Rabb
Cal's defensive play leads to points in transition

videos.description: With Cal on the offensive end, the pass drills ref David Hall that sends him flying into the crowd. The ball meanwhile bounces right to a Cal player allowed the Bears to get the basket.
videos.headline: Bank it off the ref, score two points... great idea!
Cal answers London Perrantes jumper with an and-one bucket at the other end

videos.description: With the game tied and just over a minute remaining, Isaiah Wilkins makes the tough layup and gets the foul call where he would complete the three-point play and give Virginia a lead they would never relinquish.
videos.headline: Wilkins layup and-1 puts Virginia ahead for good

videos.description: 2H (0:20) CAL Jabari Bird made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Cal cuts the Virginia lead to 2 in the final 30 seconds

videos.description: No. 12 Virginia wins its third straight game with a 56-52 victory over California.
videos.headline: Virginia slips by California to improve to 10-1
